==非晶體硼==
非晶體硼包括B<sub>12</sub> [[正二十面體|二十面體]]，會沒有固定順序的互相隨機結合<ref>{{cite journal| title = A neutron diffraction study of amorphous boron using a pulsed source| first1 = R.G. |last1=Delaplane|first2=U.|last2= Dahlborg|first3=W. S.|last3=Howells|first4=T.|last4=Lundström|journal = Journal of Non-Crystalline Solids|volume = 106| issue=1–3|year =1988| pages = 66–69| doi = 10.1016/0022-3093(88)90229-3|bibcode = 1988JNCS..106...66D |ref = harv }}</ref>。
純的非晶體硼以再1000 °C以下熱分解[[乙硼烷|乙硼烷]]生成。在1000 °C 時以退火處理會將非晶體硼轉變為β菱面体硼晶<ref>{{cite journal| title = Crystallization of Massive Amorphous Boron| author = J. S. Gillespie Jr.| journal = J. Am. Chem. Soc.| year = 1966| volume = 88|page =2423| doi = 10.1021/ja00963a011| issue = 11}}</ref>。非晶體硼的奈米線（直径30-60 nm）{{sfn|Wang |Duan|2003}} 或纖維<ref>{{cite journal| title = Microfabrication of three-dimensional boron structures by laser chemical processing| journal = J. Appl. Phys.|volume = 72| page = 5956|year =1992| doi = 10.1063/1.351904|author = S. Johansson et al.|bibcode = 1992JAP....72.5956J| issue = 12 }}</ref>可由[[濺渡沉積|濺渡沉積]]和[[雷射|雷射]]輔助[[化學氣相沉積|化學氣相沉積]]製備；也可經由1000 °C退火處理轉變為β菱面体硼晶奈米線{{sfn|Wang |Duan|2003}}。

